Added the possibility to select the changed pixels for getting back some details
that thinnning step may have gotten away. Met an old (found in 2000) bugs
of the Gimp in the process.
Added something to complete the frontiers and another to avoid killing rivers
with frontiers.
Base features : given an indexed image and a color (frontier color) in it
will make these color frontiers be one pixel thick, either in 4 connectivity
or in 8 connectivity.
